snippet.title: Trailer - The Immemorial Order II Sisters of Darkness
snippet.description:
You’ve clocked in for yet another monotonous shift at the warehouse, the scent of tobacco hanging heavily in the air. You glance at the article on your phone: “Shadows over Bricksmore.” The title sparks a flicker of excitement in your otherwise drab existence. “Is it real?” you mutter to yourself, fingers itching to explore the mystery of The Royal Immemorial Order of Ophidia further. Back home you research late into the night, but find little. Just old videos and vague rumors of gatherings deep in the woods. Frustrated but fueled by curiosity, you decide to set off on your own investigation.
